Competition: Supercopa Libertadores 
Season: 1997
* http://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Supercopa_Libertadores_1997
BlockSource: http://www.rsssf.com/sacups/supcopa97.html

* Note: the worst three clubs in the first stage will not be admitted to the Supercopa 1998.  Vasco da Gama are admitted for the first time in recognition of their winning a South American Club Championship in Santiago in 1948. Argentinos Juniors were not admitted to this year's edition, presumably due to finishing last in the three-team first round group in the 1996 Supercopa.

